There's project based ones

00:11:00.020 --> 00:11:03.660
that really will help
give students a chance

00:11:03.660 --> 00:11:07.250
to have a deeper connection to
history that sometimes we lose

00:11:07.250 --> 00:11:11.110
when we're reading it but can
definitely hear it and feel it

00:11:11.110 --> 00:11:14.660
when you hear the conversations
with members of [inaudible],

00:11:14.660 --> 00:11:18.590
with women's rights and
labor rights movements.

00:11:18.590 --> 00:11:22.090
So, anyway, we implore
you to go to the website.

00:11:22.090 --> 00:11:23.390
Have fun with it.

