across the table

00:42:53.690 --> 00:42:57.800
from some locals form
there, and Studs,

00:42:57.800 --> 00:43:01.150
he just got them
into conversation.

00:43:01.150 --> 00:43:05.060
And, just started kind
of peeling away the,

00:43:05.060 --> 00:43:08.300
what they thought about the
present state of the union.

00:43:08.300 --> 00:43:15.690
And, just because of his sort
of elfish charm and how his,

00:43:15.690 --> 00:43:20.810
