spirit in which they could bring

00:43:30.190 --> 00:43:35.710
out every vehement, you know,
vitriolic thing they had

00:43:35.710 --> 00:43:38.040
against the other side.

00:43:38.040 --> 00:43:40.170
And, there's Studs, you know,

00:43:40.170 --> 00:43:46.000
