00:47:17.360 --> 00:47:18.880
They were on the
field half the time,

00:47:18.880 --> 00:47:20.420
and the umpire shooed them off.

00:47:20.420 --> 00:47:21.720
And, they'd run back again.

00:47:21.720 --> 00:47:24.400
And, the players and
the fans were one.

00:47:24.400 --> 00:47:28.660
Now, there's a very stern
railing separates the playing

00:47:28.660 --> 00:47:31.650
field and the grandstand,
and neither one can go

00:47:31.650 --> 00:47:32.950
on the other's territory.

00:47:32.950 --> 00:47:35.650
&gt;&gt; I think this is
worth dwelling upon.

00:47:35.650 --> 00:47:36.950
Something has happened.

