01:08:46.180 --> 01:08:47.650
&gt;&gt; Matthew Barton:
Yeah, one of the jewels

01:08:47.650 --> 01:08:50.250
of our recorded sound
collection is the NBC collection

01:08:50.250 --> 01:08:51.850
which starts in 1935.

01:08:51.850 --> 01:08:55.250
And, it's tens of thousands
of hours of every kind

01:08:55.250 --> 01:08:57.620
of radio there was,
not just sports.

01:08:57.620 --> 01:09:00.530
And, NBC had a Spanish
language service,

01:09:00.530 --> 01:09:05.320
