and early 20th century were big,

01:13:59.370 --> 01:14:01.900
big influences for
Studs as well.

01:14:01.900 --> 01:14:04.700
But, not an interview
with him in the archive.

01:14:04.700 --> 01:14:06.810
The radio archive
begins in 1952,

01:14:06.810 --> 01:14:09.960
so he would have missed
out in that way, too.

